{"id": "1342890141186003027", "channel_id": "1342776198903627797", "type": 0, "author_id": "725560189981556747", "author_name": "menta_y_menta", "author_bot": false, "content": "> ﻿🎭﻿ \nRamona：山本 亜衣（Ai Yamamoto）\nOgier：音羽 里奏（Rina Otowa，English translation \"Kanade Otonari\" is incorrect❌﻿ ）\n﻿Lotan：宮園 美海（Miumi  Miyazono，English translation \"Miharu  Miyazono\" is incorrect❌﻿ ）\nDoll：魚谷 佳代（Kayo Uotani）\nTawil：山本 亜衣（Ai Yamamoto）\nNautila：國実 久留子（Kuruko Kunimi）\nKaren：二ノ宮 雪乃（Yukino Ninomiya）\n24：伊藤 さつき（Satsuki Ito）\nRyker：高仲 祐之（Hiroyuki  Takanaka，New stage name is 高仲 佑星（Yusei Takanaka），English translation \"Takanao Yuki\" is incorrect❌﻿ ）\n Hameln：野宮 一範（Nomiya Kazunori，English translation \"Kazama Nomiyasu\" is incorrect❌﻿ ）\nNymphaea：東海林 亜祐（Shoji Ayu，English translation \"Ayato Higashikawa\" is incorrect❌﻿ ）\nPandia：橘 ゆき（Yuki Tachibana）\nLily：盛 恵里花（Erika Mori，English translation \"Rika Seiei\" is incorrect❌﻿ ）\nAlva：二ノ宮 雪乃（Yukino Ninomiya）", "timestamp": "2025-02-22T16:05:59.351000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-02-22T16:21:15.117000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1342776198903627797", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "About Voice Actor", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1342890247083790378", "channel_id": "1342776198903627797", "type": 0, "author_id": "725560189981556747", "author_name": "menta_y_menta", "author_bot": false, "content": "> 🌊 \nCaecus：星乃 圭吾（Keigo Hoshino）\nMurphy：白瀬 まゆ（Mayu Shitase，English translation \"Mayumi Shirase\" is incorrect❌ ）\nCeleste：藤崎 桃子（Momoko Fujisaki）\nSanga：音羽 里奏（Rina Otowa，English translation \"Kanade Otonari\" is incorrect❌ ）\nGoliath：木下 章嗣（Akitsugu Kinoshita）\nTulu：宮園 美海（Miumi  Miyazono，English translation \"Miharu  Miyazono\" is incorrect❌ ）\nMiryam：北﨑 ひとみ（Hitomi Kitazaki）\nAurita：田村 ゆかり（Yukari Tamura）\nFaros：藤崎 桃子（Momoko Fujisaki）", "timestamp": "2025-02-22T16:06:24.599000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-02-22T16:19:24.155000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1342776198903627797", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "About Voice Actor", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1342890337613512714", "channel_id": "1342776198903627797", "type": 0, "author_id": "725560189981556747", "author_name": "menta_y_menta", "author_bot": false, "content": "> ﻿🩸﻿ \nHelot：國実 久留子（Kuruko Kunimi）\nLeigh：小坂 ほのか（Honoka  Kosaka）\n﻿﻿ Uvhash：森田 絵音（Kaito  Morita，English translation \"Morita Eon\" is incorrect❌﻿）\nAigis：山本 彩乃（Ayano Yamamoto）\n Faint：伊藤 さつき（Satsuki Ito）\n﻿Thais：山本 亜衣（Ai Yamamoto）\nAgrippa：石川 明日菜（Anna Ishikawa，English translation \"Asuka Ishikawa\" is incorrect❌﻿）\nSorel：田村ゆかり（Yukari Tamura）\nSalavdor：楠 大典（Taiten Kusunoki）", "timestamp": "2025-02-22T16:06:46.183000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-02-22T16:18:40.647000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1342776198903627797", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "About Voice Actor", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1342890506241314846", "channel_id": "1342776198903627797", "type": 0, "author_id": "725560189981556747", "author_name": "menta_y_menta", "author_bot": false, "content": "> ﻿🟪﻿ \nWinkle：七緒 凜（Rin Nanao，English translation \"Rin Nanase\" is incorrect❌﻿）\nWanda：本多 真梨子（Mariko Honda）\nHorla：橘 ゆき（Yuki Tachibana）\nLiz：青池 優花（Yuka Aoike）\nTinct：岡本 美歌（Mika Okamoto，Really sings well 😳﻿ ）\nErica：三浦 小季（Miura Saki，English translation \"Miura Koki\" is incorrect❌﻿）\nCasiah：七緒 凜（Rin Nanao，English translation \"Rin Nanase\" is incorrect❌﻿）\nJenkin：やまだまるな（Maruna Yamada）\nDaffodil：小清水 亜美（Ami Koshimizu）\n\n\n小抱怨一下，名字裡日文的部分都被硬翻成中文，反而變得好難找甚至還會找不到人<:flop:1236937860922343466> \nThe Japanese parts of the names were forcibly translated into Chinese, making them much harder to find or even impossible to locate.<:flop:1236937860922343466>", "timestamp": "2025-02-22T16:07:26.387000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-02-22T17:00:18.403000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1342776198903627797", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "About Voice Actor", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
